## Browser Support
- Support latest Chromium, Firefox, and Safari.
- IE is not supported.

## PWA / Service Worker
- Service Worker is responsible only for:
  - App Shell caching
  - Push notifications
- API responses must not be cached in Service Worker.
- Data freshness is guaranteed by TanStack Query.

## Polyfill
- Avoid global polyfills by default.
- Apply selective polyfills only when required.
- Global polyfills live in `app/polyfills.ts`.
- Import global polyfills in `app/layout.tsx`.
- Feature-specific polyfills must be dynamically imported.
- Do not place polyfills in server components or domain layers.

## SEO
- SEO applies only to public pages.
- Metadata must be defined in server components.
- CSR-only pages are excluded from SEO targets.
